1
00:00:14,733 --> 00:00:16,800
Ma'am Rina, someone's making
a scene outside!

2
00:00:16,867 --> 00:00:17,933
Who?

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,100
Come on, come with me!

4
00:00:20,167 --> 00:00:22,467
- What's going on?
- Yen! Oh my God!

5
00:00:22,533 --> 00:00:23,967
- Yen! Yen, our baby!
- What's going on?

6
00:00:24,033 --> 00:00:25,467
Move! What's going on?

7
00:00:25,533 --> 00:00:28,033
Yen! Let's bring her
to the hospital, Mom!

8
00:00:29,433 --> 00:00:31,900
Eden, you almost had
a miscarriage

9
00:00:31,967 --> 00:00:32,933
because of what happened.

10
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,000
You need a strict bed rest.

11
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:38,200
You have to avoid anything
that can stress you out,

12
00:00:38,267 --> 00:00:40,133
both physically and emotionally.

13
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:43,267
Or else your bleeding
will continue,

14
00:00:43,333 --> 00:00:45,167
and you might lose your baby.

15
00:00:45,233 --> 00:00:46,233
Eden!

16
00:00:46,300 --> 00:00:48,300
- No, Amanda!
- Eden!

17
00:00:48,367 --> 00:00:50,467
Why are you forcing your way in?

18
00:00:50,533 --> 00:00:52,033
Eden is not well!

19
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:54,433
So, please do her the favor
and just leave!

20
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:55,900
You're the stubborn one...

21
00:00:55,967 --> 00:00:57,267
I told you not to force
yourself...

22
00:00:57,333 --> 00:00:59,600
- You're hurting me!
- You're also hurting me!

23
00:00:59,667 --> 00:01:01,100
- Stop it!
- No, you stop!

24
00:01:01,167 --> 00:01:03,167
Guard! Security!

25
00:01:03,233 --> 00:01:04,200
Security!

26
00:01:04,267 --> 00:01:05,200
Let go of me!

27
00:01:05,267 --> 00:01:06,233
Get her out!
Get her out!

28
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:07,133
Mom!

29
00:01:11,667 --> 00:01:12,933
- Eden?
- Yen!

30
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:13,967
Oh my God!

31
00:01:14,033 --> 00:01:15,133
- Yen!
- Now, you see!

32
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:17,467
- What happened?
- I told you, she's not well!

33
00:01:17,533 --> 00:01:19,533
I know you want to see your mom,

34
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:23,833
but she won't do you
any good now.

35
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:26,200
It has nothing to do
with our feud.

36
00:01:26,267 --> 00:01:29,567
I know what's best
for all of us.

37
00:01:41,533 --> 00:01:44,600
She can't do this to me.

38
00:01:44,667 --> 00:01:46,667
She can't poison
my daughter's mind.

39
00:01:47,700 --> 00:01:49,400
I need to talk to Eden.

40
00:02:18,433 --> 00:02:20,100
Bernie, bring the car
around now.

41
00:02:20,167 --> 00:02:22,067
We're on our way out.

42
00:02:28,033 --> 00:02:31,600
Are you sure it's a good idea
to bring Eden home?

43
00:02:31,667 --> 00:02:34,167
Yes. Well, according
to Dr. Villegas,

44
00:02:34,233 --> 00:02:37,567
everything should be all right
as long as she has a nurse.

45
00:02:37,633 --> 00:02:40,667
Which is why I arranged for one.

46
00:02:40,733 --> 00:02:43,833
It's better to get her away
from her mom.

47
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,767
Excuse me, where's the patient
in this room?

48
00:03:05,833 --> 00:03:08,067
She's been discharged, Ma'am.

49
00:03:08,133 --> 00:03:09,733
What?

50
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,567
What time was it?
She was just here earlier.

51
00:03:11,633 --> 00:03:13,733
She had just got discharged.

52
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,700
You might still see her outside.

53
00:03:21,767 --> 00:03:24,300
Yen, are you sure you're okay?

54
00:03:24,367 --> 00:03:26,533
I'm fine.

55
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:31,533
I think it will be better
if I rest at home.

56
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:32,833
Let's go this way.

57
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:34,300
Ah, all right. Be careful.

58
00:03:34,367 --> 00:03:35,767
Yes.

59
00:03:40,167 --> 00:03:41,600
Oh, I'll get the door.

60
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:51,667
Eden!

61
00:03:56,033 --> 00:03:58,267
Eden!

62
00:03:58,333 --> 00:03:59,333
Eden, wait!

63
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:03,700
Eden, wait!

64
00:04:03,767 --> 00:04:05,333
Wait for me!

65
00:04:13,667 --> 00:04:16,867
Eden, don't leave me!

66
00:04:18,667 --> 00:04:20,233
Eden!

67
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:26,767
Eden, don't leave me! Eden!

68
00:04:36,433 --> 00:04:38,900
I am going to call security.

69
00:04:38,967 --> 00:04:41,467
I'll have that woman banned!

70
00:04:41,533 --> 00:04:42,900
Isn't that a little too much,
Mom?

71
00:04:42,967 --> 00:04:45,633
She's probably just worried
about Yenyen.

72
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:47,533
Will she come here
and make a scene

73
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,067
if she's worried about her?

74
00:04:49,133 --> 00:04:53,267
Knowing Eden's condition?

75
00:04:53,333 --> 00:04:56,467
I will call the cops on her

76
00:04:56,533 --> 00:04:58,300
if she doesn't stop
making a scene.

77
00:04:58,367 --> 00:05:00,100
Let me see my daughter.

78
00:05:00,167 --> 00:05:01,600
She's not here, Ma'am.

79
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:02,967
She's not here?

80
00:05:03,033 --> 00:05:05,567
Don't keep my daughter from me!

81
00:05:05,633 --> 00:05:07,267
Call Eden!

82
00:05:07,333 --> 00:05:08,600
I want to talk to her!

83
00:05:08,667 --> 00:05:10,233
Ma'am, you better go home

84
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:12,800
if you're only here
to make a scene.

85
00:05:12,867 --> 00:05:15,700
I won't cause a scene if you
let me see my daughter!

86
00:05:16,967 --> 00:05:18,367
Auntie, no.

87
00:05:18,433 --> 00:05:20,900
Please don't do that.

88
00:05:20,967 --> 00:05:23,467
I don't want my mom
to go to jail.

89
00:05:23,533 --> 00:05:26,233
Eden, she won't learn her
lesson if I don't do that.

90
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:28,133
I understand.

91
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,067
Just let me talk to her.

92
00:05:30,133 --> 00:05:31,100
You're going to talk to her?

93
00:05:31,167 --> 00:05:32,367
And then what?

94
00:05:32,433 --> 00:05:34,667
She's going to push you again?

95
00:05:34,767 --> 00:05:35,967
What about my grandchild?

96
00:05:36,033 --> 00:05:37,867
I know my mom.

97
00:05:37,933 --> 00:05:40,967
She won't stop
until she sees me.

98
00:05:41,033 --> 00:05:45,967
So, please, Auntie, let me talk
to her to make her understand.

99
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,567
Please, don't make a scene here,
Ma'am. Just go home.

100
00:05:54,633 --> 00:05:56,033
Let me see my daughter!

101
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:57,500
Do you understand?

102
00:05:57,567 --> 00:05:58,933
I want to talk...

103
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,000
Eden!

104
00:06:01,067 --> 00:06:02,500
Eden!

105
00:06:02,567 --> 00:06:03,700
Mom.

106
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:10,833
I'll talk to her.

107
00:06:13,267 --> 00:06:14,867
- Eden.
- Mom.

108
00:06:14,933 --> 00:06:17,400
Eden, thank you for coming out
to see me.

109
00:06:20,667 --> 00:06:24,767
I know you're not doing so well.

110
00:06:24,833 --> 00:06:30,000
Eden, I didn't mean to hurt you.

111
00:06:30,067 --> 00:06:35,533
I didn't mean to put your child
in danger.

112
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,233
I'm sorry, Eden.

113
00:06:40,067 --> 00:06:41,467
Don't worry about it, Mom.

114
00:06:41,567 --> 00:06:43,567
I don't want to think
about that now.

115
00:06:45,067 --> 00:06:52,500
Eden, I'm not comfortable
seeing you with those people.

116
00:06:52,567 --> 00:06:54,367
Eden, come with me.

117
00:06:54,433 --> 00:06:57,800
Come on, let's go home.

118
00:06:57,867 --> 00:06:59,500
Come with me. Let's go home.

119
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:06,433
I admit I'm at fault too.

120
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,533
I got mad at you,

121
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,300
especially when I found out
you were pregnant.

122
00:07:09,367 --> 00:07:10,700
But Eden,

123
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:15,167
I was just shocked.

124
00:07:15,267 --> 00:07:16,200
I got upset.

125
00:07:16,267 --> 00:07:22,167
But I can put aside my anger.

126
00:07:22,233 --> 00:07:25,267
I can do that for you, Eden.

127
00:07:28,033 --> 00:07:35,000
I just don't understand why you
chose to be with those people!

128
00:07:35,067 --> 00:07:38,700
Those people who made
my life miserable!

129
00:07:38,767 --> 00:07:41,600
Eden, come on. Come with me.

130
00:07:41,667 --> 00:07:43,733
Let's talk this out,
just the two of us.

131
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,833
Let's fix this, come on.

132
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:48,933
Come with me, Eden.

133
00:07:49,033 --> 00:07:51,233
Please.

134
00:07:55,133 --> 00:07:57,533
Mom, I'm not coming with you.

135
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,933
What do you mean you're not
coming with me?

136
00:08:12,967 --> 00:08:15,133
I'm not leaving Red.

137
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:21,167
So you're choosing him over me?

138
00:08:26,567 --> 00:08:27,800
Mom, I love you.

139
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:34,633
I want to be with you every day.

140
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:36,033
You know that, Mom.

141
00:08:37,267 --> 00:08:41,033
I'm not choosing anyone
over you.

142
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:45,200
I'm just doing what's best
for me right now, Mom.

143
00:08:45,267 --> 00:08:48,367
Eden, I'm your mom.

144
00:08:48,433 --> 00:08:49,500
I'm your mom.

145
00:08:49,567 --> 00:08:53,967
Shouldn't you care more about me
instead of that guy?

146
00:08:54,033 --> 00:08:55,833
Mom, I'm sorry.

147
00:08:55,933 --> 00:08:57,700
I don't want to hurt you.

148
00:08:57,767 --> 00:09:00,200
But I need Red
more than anything.

149
00:09:00,267 --> 00:09:03,600
Didn't I tell you that
I don't want my child

150
00:09:03,667 --> 00:09:06,200
to grow up without a father?

151
00:09:06,267 --> 00:09:08,500
I just don't want my child
to have the same life as mine.

152
00:09:08,567 --> 00:09:11,300
Eden.

153
00:09:11,367 --> 00:09:14,267
Eden...

154
00:09:14,333 --> 00:09:20,900
I know you can't accept
my child or Red.

155
00:09:20,967 --> 00:09:22,500
Eden.

156
00:09:22,567 --> 00:09:29,433
I don't want you to wake up
every day to see me

157
00:09:29,533 --> 00:09:34,000
and the result of my mistake.

158
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:43,667
I don't want to fight
with you anymore.

159
00:09:43,733 --> 00:09:47,067
I can't handle that.

160
00:09:47,133 --> 00:09:50,033
My pregnancy is very fragile.

161
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:53,233
And I'm not blaming you for it.

162
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:55,033
I'm not blaming you.

163
00:09:58,100 --> 00:10:02,900
But it will be better
if I stay here for now.

164
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,800
Eden.

165
00:10:04,867 --> 00:10:07,500
Eden, please don't do this
to me.

166
00:10:07,567 --> 00:10:10,633
Eden, don't do this to me.

167
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:16,100
I'm begging you. Please
don't do this to me.

168
00:10:16,167 --> 00:10:18,433
Red's family accepts me.

169
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:23,667
And that's what I need
right now.

170
00:10:23,733 --> 00:10:27,867
Until you accept my pregnancy
or Red,

171
00:10:27,933 --> 00:10:32,567
it will be better for me
to be away from you.

172
00:10:32,633 --> 00:10:33,767
I'll stay away from you,
for now, Mom.

173
00:10:33,833 --> 00:10:36,833
For my child's safety.

174
00:10:36,933 --> 00:10:39,700
I hope you understand.

175
00:10:39,767 --> 00:10:43,300
Are you getting me out
of your life?

176
00:10:43,367 --> 00:10:45,467
No, Mom.

177
00:10:45,533 --> 00:10:47,833
I'm not doing that.

178
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:52,200
I just need to think about
my child, my pregnancy.

179
00:10:54,633 --> 00:10:58,633
I can't be stressed right now.

180
00:10:58,700 --> 00:10:59,633
I'm sorry, Mom.

181
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:01,933
Stressed?

182
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:04,333
Am I stressing you out?

183
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:09,033
Didn't you say you're not
blaming me for what happened?

184
00:11:09,133 --> 00:11:16,567
Then why are you saying
that I'm causing you trouble?

185
00:11:16,633 --> 00:11:17,567
Mom...

186
00:11:17,633 --> 00:11:21,567
Eden, why are you choosing
them over me?

187
00:11:21,633 --> 00:11:25,500
You're hurting me!

188
00:11:25,567 --> 00:11:28,567
It hurts!

189
00:11:28,633 --> 00:11:34,633
It hurts to hear this from you.

190
00:11:36,833 --> 00:11:40,267
What did they feed you?

191
00:11:40,333 --> 00:11:42,200
What kind of spell did they cast
on you?

192
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:44,367
What kind of potion did they use
on you for you

193
00:11:44,433 --> 00:11:47,833
to hurt me like this?

194
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:51,833
For you to disrespect me?

195
00:11:51,900 --> 00:11:54,300
Acceptance, Mom.

196
00:11:54,367 --> 00:11:56,600
Understanding.

197
00:11:56,667 --> 00:11:58,333
And care...

198
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:01,033
that I thought I'd get from you!

199
00:12:01,100 --> 00:12:04,600
Because I've wanted
that for so long!

200
00:12:04,667 --> 00:12:06,900
But I was wrong.

201
00:12:16,867 --> 00:12:19,233
You're not my daughter!

202
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:22,067
You're not Eden!

203
00:12:22,133 --> 00:12:26,333
My daughter won't say that to
me!

204
00:12:30,467 --> 00:12:31,433
Eden!

205
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:34,667
Eden!

206
00:12:34,733 --> 00:12:38,133
I'm sorry for kicking you out.

207
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,800
I'm sorry.

208
00:12:39,867 --> 00:12:43,000
I'm sorry for hurting you.

209
00:12:43,067 --> 00:12:45,267
I'll ask you for forgiveness
over and over.

210
00:12:45,333 --> 00:12:48,433
Just tell me what I have to do.

211
00:12:48,533 --> 00:12:50,300
Mom, I have forgiven you.

212
00:12:50,367 --> 00:12:52,700
I just need one thing right now.

213
00:12:52,767 --> 00:12:54,700
Just let me stay here for now.

214
00:12:54,767 --> 00:12:57,833
Eden, this is so painful.

215
00:12:57,900 --> 00:13:00,800
Don't do this. Don't do this
to me, Eden.

216
00:13:05,533 --> 00:13:09,100
Red, will you please
just calm down?

217
00:13:09,167 --> 00:13:13,267
Rina, why did you let her talk
to Amanda?

218
00:13:13,333 --> 00:13:15,300
What if Amanda causes trouble
again?

219
00:13:15,367 --> 00:13:18,167
What will happen
to Eden's child?

220
00:13:18,233 --> 00:13:19,867
Eden wanted to talk to her.

221
00:13:19,933 --> 00:13:23,600
And don't worry. She said Amanda
wouldn't mess with us anymore

222
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:26,767
after they talked.

223
00:13:26,833 --> 00:13:28,933
How can you be so sure?

224
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,967
You know Amanda.

225
00:13:31,033 --> 00:13:32,667
It's her hobby to cause trouble.

226
00:13:32,733 --> 00:13:37,200
Well, I trust Eden.

227
00:13:37,267 --> 00:13:41,500
She's the only person
who can handle Amanda.

228
00:13:45,033 --> 00:13:47,600
I'm not at ease that Yenyen
is with her mom.

229
00:13:47,667 --> 00:13:49,933
What if something bad
happens to her?

230
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,967
I'm sorry, Mom. But I have
to protect her.

231
00:13:52,033 --> 00:13:54,733
Red, Red!

232
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:59,133
Eden, you're hurting me.

233
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:02,933
Don't do this. Don't do this
to me, Eden.

234
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:06,300
Please, don't do this to me.
I can't bear it.

235
00:14:06,367 --> 00:14:08,567
I can't bear it, Eden.

236
00:14:08,633 --> 00:14:09,767
Mom...

237
00:14:09,833 --> 00:14:12,167
I admit I've done something
wrong. I did you wrong.

238
00:14:12,233 --> 00:14:16,700
But Eden, don't push me away
like this!

239
00:14:16,767 --> 00:14:20,433
Please, Eden! I can't bear this.

240
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:23,633
- Mom.
- Eden, come on.

241
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:29,500
Come with me. I'm begging you.

242
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:32,300
Please, come on.
Just come with me.

243
00:14:32,367 --> 00:14:33,967
Let's go home.

244
00:14:34,033 --> 00:14:36,300
I'm not asking you to go away.

245
00:14:36,367 --> 00:14:39,033
I'm not cutting you off.

246
00:14:39,100 --> 00:14:41,667
Eden.

247
00:14:41,733 --> 00:14:42,800
You're still my mom.

248
00:14:42,867 --> 00:14:44,533
It won't change.

249
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:49,333
But I just need to stay here
for now.

250
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:53,833
Because this is not healthy
for me, Mom.

251
00:14:53,900 --> 00:14:56,533
I can't let you stay here.

252
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,967
You have to come with me!

253
00:14:58,033 --> 00:15:00,100
I'm taking you home with me.

254
00:15:00,167 --> 00:15:01,433
Come on, Eden.

255
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:02,567
You have to come with me.

256
00:15:02,667 --> 00:15:06,033
I'm begging you. I'm getting you
away from this place!

257
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:07,667
Please, Eden.

258
00:15:07,733 --> 00:15:10,467
Mom, I'm sorry.

259
00:15:10,533 --> 00:15:11,467
I'm sorry, Mom.

260
00:15:11,533 --> 00:15:14,233
Eden. Don't do this.

261
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:16,600
Don't do this to me, Eden.

262
00:15:16,667 --> 00:15:19,300
Mom, stop.

263
00:15:19,367 --> 00:15:21,600
- Yen, Yen!
- Let's go home.

264
00:15:21,667 --> 00:15:23,767
Mom, you're hurting me.

265
00:15:23,833 --> 00:15:24,767
- Open the gate.
- Miss Amanda,

266
00:15:24,833 --> 00:15:25,933
please let go of her.

267
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,367
- I'm taking my daughter home.
- Please let her go.

268
00:15:27,433 --> 00:15:29,733
- I'm taking my daughter home!
- You have to leave!

269
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:31,767
I can't bear this, Eden.

270
00:15:31,833 --> 00:15:33,333
I can't bear this!

271
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:36,233
You should leave, Miss Amanda.

272
00:15:36,333 --> 00:15:37,933
- Yenyen.
- Mom, please, leave.

273
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,700
Don't cause any trouble, Mom.
Just go home.

274
00:15:40,767 --> 00:15:42,400
I love you so much.

275
00:15:42,467 --> 00:15:46,267
- You should go home, Mom.
- Come with me. Let's go home.

276
00:15:46,333 --> 00:15:47,600
Miss Amanda, you should go home.

277
00:15:47,667 --> 00:15:48,967
Red, let my daughter come home
with me, please!

278
00:15:49,033 --> 00:15:51,800
- Please go home.
- Let her come home with me!

279
00:15:51,867 --> 00:15:54,033
- It's better...
- She's better off staying here.

280
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:55,267
Mom, this is for your own good.

281
00:15:55,333 --> 00:15:57,933
They're poisoning your mind.

282
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:01,033
Don't believe their lies, Eden.

283
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:02,567
Come on, come with me.

284
00:16:02,633 --> 00:16:05,933
Red, take her inside.

285
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:06,967
Let me bring her home.

286
00:16:07,033 --> 00:16:08,300
Take her inside.

287
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:10,800
Give me back my daughter!

288
00:16:10,867 --> 00:16:13,300
Give her back to me!

289
00:16:13,367 --> 00:16:15,533
Yenyen!

290
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:16,933
Eden!

291
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,500
Amanda, please,
stop causing a scene!

292
00:16:18,567 --> 00:16:20,533
Please, leave!

293
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,167
You monsters!

294
00:16:22,233 --> 00:16:24,233
Give me back my daughter!

295
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:28,767
Don't take her away from me!

296
00:16:28,833 --> 00:16:32,467
Amanda, don't make me call
the police.

297
00:16:32,533 --> 00:16:33,467
Go home!

298
00:16:33,533 --> 00:16:35,900
Victor, I'm begging you.

299
00:16:35,967 --> 00:16:37,633
I'm begging you, please.

300
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:40,833
Give me back my daughter! Eden!

301
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:43,667
Eden!

302
00:16:43,767 --> 00:16:47,667
Let's go home! Eden!

303
00:16:47,733 --> 00:16:51,100
Please, don't do this to me!

304
00:16:52,167 --> 00:16:54,200
I can't bear this!

305
00:16:54,267 --> 00:16:58,333
I can't bear this pain, Eden!

306
00:17:00,733 --> 00:17:03,900
Give her back to me!

307
00:17:03,967 --> 00:17:05,967
Eden!

308
00:17:06,033 --> 00:17:08,400
Eden, I love you, my child!

309
00:17:08,467 --> 00:17:12,100
Eden!

310
00:17:14,867 --> 00:17:17,000
Eden!

311
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:41,833
Emma told me that your mom
had just left.

312
00:17:43,567 --> 00:17:45,933
I feel guilty, Red.

313
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,900
I feel like I didn't do
the right thing.

314
00:17:57,267 --> 00:17:58,900
Yen, I understand
how you're feeling.

315
00:18:00,567 --> 00:18:03,100
But sometimes, we have to stand
our ground.

316
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:07,533
I'm so selfish.

317
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:12,100
I didn't think about my mom's
feelings.

318
00:18:13,867 --> 00:18:15,833
Red, this is the first time
I've had a fight with her

319
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:19,100
in my entire life.

320
00:18:19,167 --> 00:18:22,567
Even though she was not always
with me growing up,

321
00:18:22,667 --> 00:18:27,900
we were always happy to see
each other.

322
00:18:27,967 --> 00:18:31,900
I thought we'd become closer
once she got out of jail.

323
00:18:31,967 --> 00:18:36,567
But I feel like we're
drifting apart.

324
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:45,733
Yen, I'm sorry.

325
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:50,167
Because I'm the reason you two
are fighting.

326
00:18:50,233 --> 00:18:57,067
I sometimes wish I didn't
meet you.

327
00:18:57,167 --> 00:19:03,533
But I never regret loving you.

328
00:19:07,967 --> 00:19:11,100
I'll be by your side until
we fix everything.

329
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:15,033
We'll correct everything
we did wrong.

330
00:19:15,100 --> 00:19:19,600
Wrong things in the eyes
of other people, of your mom.

331
00:19:19,667 --> 00:19:21,000
Okay?

332
00:19:22,033 --> 00:19:23,633
Thank you, Red.

333
00:19:28,300 --> 00:19:31,333
And don't ever think that you
made the wrong choice

334
00:19:31,433 --> 00:19:34,933
of choosing our baby.

335
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:38,467
I think we should prioritize
our baby for now.

336
00:19:38,533 --> 00:19:41,800
Because once our baby's here,
he'll fix everything.

337
00:19:41,867 --> 00:19:43,633
Trust me.

338
00:19:55,667 --> 00:19:59,233
My own daughter abandoned me.

339
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:17,200
She chose that family over me.

340
00:21:59,467 --> 00:22:00,700
Hey, guys, guys.

341
00:22:00,767 --> 00:22:02,367
Look, look, look, look.

342
00:22:02,433 --> 00:22:05,433
- T-Rex?
- T-Rex?

343
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:08,600
It's not just T-Rex.
It's cutie-saurus.

344
00:22:08,667 --> 00:22:10,733
Look what we got here.

345
00:23:04,367 --> 00:23:06,100
Eden is happy now.

346
00:23:06,167 --> 00:23:07,800
My daughter is happy now.

347
00:23:07,867 --> 00:23:10,100
She doesn't need me anymore.

348
00:23:10,167 --> 00:23:11,900
Eden doesn't need me anymore.

349
00:23:11,967 --> 00:23:14,433
I've already found her weakness.

350
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:17,733
Her very own precious Eden.

351
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:21,233
Now I want to see how far
she can go.

352
00:23:21,300 --> 00:23:23,000
I want to drain her strength...

353
00:23:23,100 --> 00:23:27,967
until she's left with nothing.

354
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:33,100
This is it, Amanda!

355
00:23:33,167 --> 00:23:36,933
This will be your new home!

356
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:40,300
Rina, do you want me
to kill her now?
